                    <item xml:id="a25">
                    <locus target="#88v #89r" facs="089"/>
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    a closing prayer mentions original owner, <foreign xml:lang="gez">[አለ]ቀ  ኤዎስጣቴዎስ</foreign>, and his wife, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወለተ ቅደሳን</foreign>. The name of the original owner is effaced and overwritten with <foreign xml:lang="gez">አሰትእ ኢየሱስ</foreign>. Another name, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወለተ ማርያም</foreign>, is written over the place where the original owner’s wife’s name had been.  It was in turn overwritten with <foreign xml:lang="gez">አስከለ ድን[ግ]ል</foreign> in small black letters
                    </desc>
                    </item>
